      <title>斯塔默计划修改法律，简化英国与欧盟规则的衔接</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-plans-law-change-to-simplify-uk-alignment-with-eu-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默政府计划修改英国法律，使其更容易与欧盟的产品标准保持一致，这是国王演讲中提出的立法议程所包含的重大转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-plans-law-change-to-simplify-uk-alignment-with-eu-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>JCPenney 首席执行官：商店是购物体验的重要组成部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-17/jcpenney-ceo-stores-important-to-shopping-experience-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[JCPenney 首席执行官 Marc Rosen 讨论了该公司 10 亿美元再投资计划的进展、实体店对其业务的重要性以及通货膨胀如何影响零售商的客户。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-17/jcpenney-ceo-stores-important-to-shopping-experience-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的 Rubner 表示，回调开始后“不要逢低买入”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/goldman-s-rubner-says-not-buying-the-dip-as-correction-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团战术策略师斯科特·鲁布纳 (Scott Rubner) 表示，标准普尔 500 指数今后只会下跌，他警告称“我不会买入逢低买入”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/goldman-s-rubner-says-not-buying-the-dip-as-correction-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抵押贷款机构面临规则检查自动估值模型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/mortgage-lenders-face-rule-checking-automated-valuation-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[住房抵押贷款机构将必须满足一套新的标准，以确保其基于技术的评估流程不会出现缺陷，从而产生错误的估算或歧视借款人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/mortgage-lenders-face-rule-checking-automated-valuation-models</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃勒称美联储“接近”降息，但尚未实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/waller-says-fed-getting-closer-to-cutting-rates-not-there-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒表示，经济正越来越接近央行可以降低借贷成本的水平，但他表示希望看到“更多证据”表明通胀处于持续下降的轨道上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/waller-says-fed-getting-closer-to-cutting-rates-not-there-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 13:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
